{"tid":1576291,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金義聖調景嶺拍人鏈","createTime":"2019-09-17T07:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T07:29:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"623dd5f8927d94eb0b11edf5d974df9b6b670fbd","tid":1576291,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190917/20769441\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190917%2F20769441&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=4f1333d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190917%2F20769441&h=77af267c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190917/20769441</a><br />\n<br />\n金義聖調景嶺拍人鏈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190917/large/1568640183_38fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190917%2Flarge%2F1568640183_38fa.jpg&h=19f8eb05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金義聖昨晚再在沙田拍攝人鏈。<br />\n<br />\n韓片《屍殺列車》男星金義聖，自反送中運動爆發後，一直關心香港情況，前日他更在港與韓國MBC新聞節目《探查企劃 Straight》攝製隊一齊踩入灣仔、金鐘等地採訪。即使面對警方以水炮車驅散群眾又施放催淚彈，金義聖都未有退縮，更堅拒戴上「豬嘴」，直言以前經常吸催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【蘋聞重溫】《信報》拒開天窗即停寫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190917/large/1568640181_3f2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190917%2Flarge%2F1568640181_3f2e.jpg&h=758df635&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n威爾斯醫院<br />\n金義聖昨日分別到調景嶺及沙田威爾斯醫院拍攝，還開Ig直播。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190917/large/1568640182_99f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190917%2Flarge%2F1568640182_99f2.jpg&h=12aaf51f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n調景嶺<br />\n<br />\n金義聖前晚大約拍攝至晚上7時，就回酒店整理影片，他安頓後不忘向網民宣傳香港的情況，上載一張寫上「Five Demands Not one less」的照片上Ig，並留言：「I was there」。金義聖今次預計來港拍攝數日，昨早他又出動，先去調景嶺拍攝學生組織人鏈及叫口號，隨後又到沙田威爾斯親王醫院拍攝，他還開Ig做直播，由人鏈的起始拍到「龍尾」，好讓更多網民更了解香港年輕人如何和平抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：翁可人 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【傳統名校】精英遍佈各界<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n梁朝偉孖跌膊女打邊爐<br />\n<br />\n【蘋聞重溫】《信報》拒開天窗即停寫<br />\n【染紅校長】夫為財庫局局長劉怡翔<br />\n【傳統名校】精英遍佈各界<br />\n不忿學生被屈築人鏈換午餐王迪詩怒斥女拔校長污衊師妹毀校譽"},{"pid":"5ae36d7d7986c555fb00c5164bc074bcfa66b262","tid":1576291,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"ff780d79f4d224695a522c086dd13f972b795bf0","tid":1576291,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762492996d241ad365129932591db543a474dd27","tid":1576291,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:29:36.000Z","msg":"最右藍衫係咪pepe女護士？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}